{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-detail-tsx","path":"/project/css-scan","webpackCompilationHash":"e59d3f6df542cc34ed00","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"童话说","keywords":["tonghuashuo","github","front-end","javascript","typescript","react","node","washington","hua","童话","童话说","前端","博客","技术","计算机","互联网"]}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>CSS Scan</h1>\n<h2>简介</h2>\n<p>FBC 会员服务 Web App，设计用于微信端，会员可通过该 App 进行会议室预约、吧台自助消费等会员服务。</p>\n<p>基于 Vue 2.x 开发的 SPA，基于 Axios 封装了 HTTP 客户端，使用 SCSS + PostCSS 编写样式，使用 Karma + Mocha 进行单元测试，使用 Webpack 进行构建，使用 ESLint 统一代码风格。</p>\n<p>项目整体量级较轻，交互也不复杂，因此我并没有采用 Vuex，而是直接使用 LocalStorage 来进行数据缓存。利用 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">&lt;transition&gt;</code> 组件实现路由切换时的动效，模拟了原生 App 的页面切换逻辑。利用 Webpack 的 Code Split 特性实现了组件的异步加载，优化加载时间。</p>\n<h2>周期</h2>\n<p>2019 年 6 月 - 2019 年 7 月</p>\n<h2>相关链接</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://app.futurebusinesslab.com/wap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">线上地址</a></p>\n<h2>项目截图</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d2b8722933ee6c43bd359220d71bb33b/a296c/unreleased.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"项目截图\"\n        title=\"项目截图\"\n        src=\"/static/d2b8722933ee6c43bd359220d71bb33b/a296c/unreleased.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d2b8722933ee6c43bd359220d71bb33b/3bc27/unreleased.jpg 240w,\n/static/d2b8722933ee6c43bd359220d71bb33b/98431/unreleased.jpg 480w,\n/static/d2b8722933ee6c43bd359220d71bb33b/a296c/unreleased.jp